metadata.description: ***Minting is currently live here: https://soupducks.com.***  *Exclusive offering: AI-generated SupDucks oil paintings*. SupDucks are among the most actively traded and valuable NFT collections.  Rare Ducks command hundreds of thousands of dollars, and even “floor” Ducks fetch tens of thousands.  Today, the active SupDucks community has affectionately started a meme around “SoupDucks.” Through this limited offering, you are now able to mint spectacular AI-generated oil paintings of the full “SoupDucks” collection.  Employing over 100 AI technologies, this gorgeous collection allows connoisseurs to enjoy SupDucks like never before, with vibrant colors, textures, and detail.  Mint before they’re gone, then sell, trade, collect, or use however you would like during this era of explosive metaverse growth. Only one minting is available for each of the 9,999 SupDucks, with every owner receiving an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain. Get these collectibles while you still can.
